com.dlsc.flexgantt.command.eventline

Class DefaultDeleteMultipleEventlineObjectsCommand

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.dlsc.flexgantt.command.AbstractCommand
      • com.dlsc.flexgantt.command.AbstractCompoundCommand<DefaultDeleteEventlineObjectCommand>
        • com.dlsc.flexgantt.command.eventline.DefaultDeleteMultipleEventlineObjectsCommand
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ICommand, Serializable

    public class DefaultDeleteMultipleEventlineObjectsCommand
extends AbstractCompoundCommand<DefaultDeleteEventlineObjectCommand>
    A command that is used to delete several eventline objects from the eventline model at the same time. This command can only be used in situations where the model is an instance of DefaultEventlineModel and the eventline objects implement the IEventlineObject interface.
    Since:
    1.1
